					</div>
					<div class="large-6 columns text-paragraph">
						<div class="about-text">
							<h3>Mentor. Speaker. Attorney. Writer.</h3>
							<p>I'm passionate about helping others achieve their best.</p>
							<p>I'm an avid reader, learner, and student. I read a book a week or mroe. You should too. There's not much Im unwilling to try if I think that I can learn from it.</p>
							<p>When not spending time with my family, I enjoy working out, watching TED Talks, or trying to teach myself computer programming.</p> 
							<p>If I can be any help to you, please let me know. Lou Holtz once said, "The greatest compliment you can give someone is to tell them, 'You made a difference'" Accordingly, I'm always looking for such an opportunity. I'm interested in meeting new people and helping them to connect with others that may be able to help them reach that next level in whatever they are working on, personal, professional, or otherwise.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
