				<div class="row"> 
				<div class="large-5 columns">	
					<div id="long-bio">
						<h3>Long Bio...</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			</div>
			<div id="about-row-2"
				<div class="row">
					<div class="large-6 columns text-paragraph">
						<div class="about-text">
							<p>Born and raised just outside of Dayton, Ohio, I've been a life-long mid-westerner. A "towny" of sorts, I attended the University of Dayton for both undergrad and law school.</p>
							<p>In college I studied Political Science, but focused my study and course work on Leadership, Psychology, and decision making. I was intrigued by how some people, whether it be natural charisma or dogged perseverance, could motivate others to achieve more than they themselves even though possible. While in college, I joined an organization that changed my life: SigEp. In the Fraternity I was exposed to great leaders, mentors, and friends that challenged me to strive for excellence in all I did.</p>
							<p>After college, and I spent a short period of time in management and retail.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
